1.2 Data input

final <- read.csv(file = "/Users/tili/Desktop/Cell_line_bulk_seq_202011/results/tables/DES/sig_0_05_DE_genes_DES6_primary.csv", header = T, sep = ",")
final_shrunk <- read.csv(file = "/Users/tili/Desktop/Cell_line_bulk_seq_202011/results/tables/DES/sig_0_05_DE_genes_shrunk_DES6_primary.csv", header = T, sep = ",")
all <- read.csv(file = "/Users/tili/Desktop/Cell_line_bulk_seq_202011/results/tables/DES/background_genes_shrunk_DES6_primary.csv", header = T, sep = ",")

genelist <- all %>% 
  dplyr::select(entrezgene_id, log2FoldChange) 

List <- genelist$log2FoldChange
names(List) <- as.character(genelist$entrezgene_id)
List <- sort(List, decreasing = T)

1.3 GO analysis

ego <- enrichGO(gene = final_shrunk$geneID, universe = all$geneID, keyType = "ENSEMBL",
                OrgDb = org.Hs.eg.db, ont = "ALL", pAdjustMethod = "BH", 
                qvalueCutoff = 0.1, readable = TRUE)

cluster_summary <- data.frame(ego)

1.5 Msigdb gene set analysis

# msigdbr_species()
# msigdbr_collections()

msigHs_c2 <- msigdbr(species = "Homo sapiens", category = "C2") %>%
  select(gs_name, entrez_gene) %>% 
  as.data.frame()

msigHs_h <- msigdbr(species = "Homo sapiens", category = "H") %>%
  select(gs_name, entrez_gene) %>% 
  as.data.frame()

enrich <- enricher(gene = all$entrezgene_id, TERM2GENE = msigHs_h,
                   pvalueCutoff = 0.05,
                   pAdjustMethod = "BH",
                   minGSSize = 10,
                   maxGSSize = 500)
enrich <- data.frame(enrich) %>% 
  select(GeneRatio, BgRatio, pvalue, p.adjust, qvalue, geneID, Count)
knitr::kable(enrich)
